{"id":367140,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":4,"day":21}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"工厂的一日(笔会专辑)","column":"笔会专辑","genre":"","count":"107","ytitle":"","mtitle":"爱厂如家","ftitle":"","authors":["程正明"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"王老伯，年纪老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清早就往厂里跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东看看，西瞧瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起扫帚把地扫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫你一声王老伯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为啥起得这样早?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小姑娘，听分晓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前年退休来养老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器不用要生锈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不干活也难熬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂是我爹娘家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不到工厂往哪跑?"}]}